        }
        """
        When we patch "/contacts/1"
        """
        {"twitter": ""}
        """
        Then we get updated response
        """
        {
            "last_name" : "Foo", "first_name" : "Mary", "twitter": ""
        }
        """
        When we patch "/contacts/1"
        """
        {"twitter": "foo"}
        """
